Spud Monday
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:the first Monday in August when Nelsonians traditionally plant early potatoes.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
